1506490/extras/927f955486e256cc86b8680652ec37df.mp4?t=1610863290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506490/extras/3b8a70e509c154657bb6b267fabdf698.avif?t=1610863290\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\t参加激烈而残酷的枪战。让某人脑浆四溢将成为你生活中习以为常的一部分。<br></li><li>\t完成致命的徒手搏斗。把那些违背你意愿的人直接送进坟墓。<br></li><li>\t从别人的口中获得一切需要的信息和口供。可以用你的拳头，或者更有趣的东西。<br></li><li>\t观察，分析，等待惊喜从天而降。如果一个老伙计突然用枪指着你的头呢？<br></li><li>\t始终保持警觉，迅速做出决定。哪怕是短暂的一秒钟，都将起到决定性的作用。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506490/extras/42437102ee5460698a90511e11eead2e.poster.avif?t=1610863290\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506490/extras/42437102ee5460698a90511e11eead2e.webm?t=1610863290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506490/extras/42437102ee5460698a90511e11eead2e.mp4?t=1610863290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
